scripts.publishAll: echo 'publish new version trident-cli and trident to wnpm' && npm version patch && npm publish && cd global-cli && npm version patch && npm publish
scripts.wpublishAll: echo 'publish new version trident-cli and trident to wnpm' && npm version patch && wnpm publish && cd global-cli && npm version patch && wnpm publish
scripts.reinstallCli: echo 'reinstall the newest trident-cli' && npm uninstall @webank/trident-cli -g && npm install @webank/trident-cli -g
